<p align="left" class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: left; line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#000000"><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt"><span style="mso-spacerun: yes">                       </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '¸¼Àº °íµñ'; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin">↓<span style="mso-spacerun: yes">   </span></span><span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt">[Site Visit : hospitals, cities or counties]<o:p></o:p></span></font></font></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="line-height: 150%; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt">
<span lang="EN-US" style="line-height: 150%; font-family: 'times new roman', 'serif'; font-size: 12pt"><o:p><font color="#000000" face="Times New Roman"> </font></o:p></span></p>
